{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Example: Comparing Current vs. Optimized Picker Routing\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook demonstrates how to use `wms-optlab` to compare different picker routing strategies for a single order. We will:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Load warehouse data and define a sample order.\n",
    "2. Assume a simple, naive routing policy (e.g., sequence as is in the order list).\n",
    "3. Generate an optimized route using the S-shape heuristic.\n",
    "4. Calculate the travel distance for both routes and compare them.\n",
    "5. Visualize both routes on the warehouse layout."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "from wms_optlab.data.adapters_erp import load_generic_erp_data\n",
    "from wms_optlab.routing.policies import get_s_shape_route\n",
    "from wms_optlab.routing.shortest_path import calculate_route_distance\n",
    "from wms_optlab.layout.topology import create_warehouse_graph\n",
    "from wms_optlab.layout.visualization import plot_warehouse_layout"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Load Data and Define a Sample Order"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "skus_df = pd.read_csv('data/sample_skus.csv')\n",
    "locations_df = pd.read_csv('data/sample_locations.csv')\n",
    "orders_df = pd.read_csv('data/sample_orders.csv')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create the main warehouse model\n",
    "warehouse = load_generic_erp_data(skus_df, locations_df, orders_df)\n",
    "warehouse_graph = create_warehouse_graph(warehouse.locations)\n",
    "\n",
    "# For this example, let's create a slotting plan manually\n",
    "# In a real scenario, this would be the output of a slotting optimization\n",
    "storage_locs = [loc for loc in warehouse.locations if loc.location_type == 'storage']\n",
    "slotting_plan = {sku.sku_id: loc.loc_id for sku, loc in zip(warehouse.skus, storage_locs)}\n",
    "\n",
    "# Select a sample order to route\n",
    "sample_order = warehouse.orders[0]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Get the locations to visit for this order\n",
    "pick_loc_ids = [slotting_plan.get(line.sku.sku_id) for line in sample_order.order_lines]\n",
    "pick_loc_ids = [loc_id for loc_id in pick_loc_ids if loc_id]\n",
    "\n",
    "loc_map = {loc.loc_id: loc for loc in warehouse.locations}\n",
    "pick_locations = [loc_map[loc_id] for loc_id in pick_loc_ids]\n",
    "\n",
    "depot_loc = next(loc for loc in warehouse.locations if loc.location_type == 'depot')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Routing for Order: {sample_order.order_id}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Locations to visit: {pick_loc_ids}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Define and Evaluate a Naive Route"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# A naive route might just be Depot -> Pick_1 -> Pick_2 -> ... -> Depot\n",
    "naive_route = [depot_loc.loc_id] + pick_loc_ids + [depot_loc.loc_id]\n",
    "\n",
    "naive_distance = calculate_route_distance(naive_route, warehouse_graph)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Naive Route: {\' -> \'.join(naive_route)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Naive Route Distance: {naive_distance:.2f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Generate and Evaluate an S-Shape Route"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Generate the route using the S-shape heuristic\n",
    "s_shape_route = get_s_shape_route(pick_locations, warehouse_graph, depot_loc)\n",
    "\n",
    "s_shape_distance = calculate_route_distance(s_shape_route, warehouse_graph)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"S-Shape Route: {\' -> \'.join(s_shape_route)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"S-Shape Route Distance: {s_shape_distance:.2f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "improvement = ((naive_distance - s_shape_distance) / naive_distance) * 100 if naive_distance > 0 else 0\n",
    "print(f\"\nImprovement: {improvement:.2f}%\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Visualize the Routes"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plot_warehouse_layout(",
    "    warehouse_graph,",
    "    route=naive_route,",
    "    title='Warehouse Layout with Naive Picking Route'"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plot_warehouse_layout(",
    "    warehouse_graph,",
    "    route=s_shape_route,",
    "    title='Warehouse Layout with S-Shape Optimized Route'"
   ]
  }
 ],
